params.sqlcmd: "select " +" M_ITEM.\\"ITEM_CD\\" as \\"ITEM_CD\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"ITEM_NAME\\" as \\"ITEM_NAME\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"DRAW_CD\\" as \\"DRAW_CD\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"SPEC\\" as \\"SPEC\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"MRP_ODR_TYP\\" as \\"MRP_ODR_TYP\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"OUTSIDE_TYP\\" as \\"OUTSIDE_TYP\\" " +"from " +" M_ITEM " +"where " +" M_ITEM.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ?"

"select " +" M_ITEM.\\"ITEM_CD\\" as \\"ITEM_CD\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"ITEM_NAME\\" as \\"ITEM_NAME\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"DRAW_CD\\" as \\"DRAW_CD\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"SPEC\\" as \\"SPEC\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"MRP_ODR_TYP\\" as \\"MRP_ODR_TYP\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"OUTSIDE_TYP\\" as \\"OUTSIDE_TYP\\" " +"from " +" M_ITEM " +"where " +" M_ITEM.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ?"
"select " +" SYS_MY_COMPANY.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" as \\"COMPANY_CD\\" " +"from " +" SYS_MY_COMPANY " +"where " +" SYS_MY_COMPANY.\\"CTRL_CD\\" = 'SYSTEM'"

"select " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"PROC_CD\\" as \\"PROC_CD\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"PROC_NAME\\" as \\"PROC_NAME\\" " +"from " +" M_PROC_GRP " +"where " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_PROC_GRP.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_PROC_GRP.\\"PROC_CD\\" = ?"

"select " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"PROC_CD\\" as \\"PROC_CD\\" " +"from " +" M_PROC_GRP " +"where " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_PROC_GRP.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_PROC_GRP.\\"PROC_CD\\" = ?"

"select " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"VEND_CD\\" as \\"VEND_CD\\", " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"VEND_ANAME\\" as \\"VEND_ANAME\\", " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"CUR_CD\\" as \\"CUR_CD\\", " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"ROUND_TYP\\" as \\"ROUND_TYP\\", " +" M_CUR.\\"CUR_NAME\\" as \\"CUR_NAME\\", " +" M_CUR.\\"DECIMAL_FIG\\" as \\"DECIMAL_FIG\\" " +"from " +" M_VEND_CTRL, " +" M_CUR " +"where " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_VEND_CTRL.\\"VEND_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_VEND_CTRL.\\"CUR_CD\\" = M_CUR.\\"CUR_CD\\"(+)"
"select " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"VEND_CD\\" as \\"VEND_CD\\" " +"from " +" M_VEND_CTRL " +"where " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_VEND_CTRL.\\"VEND_CD\\" = ?"

"select " +" M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST_H.\\"VEND_ITEM_CD\\" as \\"VEND_ITEM_CD\\", " +" M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST_H.\\"MODIFY_COUNT\\" as \\"MODIFY_COUNT\\" " +"from " +" M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST_H " +"where " +" M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST_H.\\"VEND_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST_H.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST_H.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST_H.\\"PROC_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST_H.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ?"

"select " +" TO_CHAR(M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"EFF_PHASE_IN_DATE\\", 'YYYY/MM/DD') as \\"EFF_PHASE_IN_DATE\\", " +" M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"UNIT_COST\\" as \\"UNIT_COST\\", " +" M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"UNIT_COST_TYP\\" as \\"UNIT_COST_TYP\\", " +" M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"PROCESSING_COST\\" as \\"PROCESSING_COST\\", " +" M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"MATERIAL_COST\\" as \\"MATERIAL_COST\\", " +" M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"OTHER_OVERHEADS\\" as \\"OTHER_OVERHEADS\\", " +" M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"MODIFY_COUNT\\" as \\"MODIFY_COUNT\\" " +"from " +" M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST " +"where " +" M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"VEND_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"PROC_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"SBCNT_SIZE\\" = 0 " +"order by " +" M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"EFF_PHASE_IN_DATE\\""

"insert into " +" M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST(\\"COMPANY_CD\\", \\"VEND_CD\\", \\"PLANT_CD\\", \\"ITEM_CD\\", \\"PROC_CD\\", \\"EFF_PHASE_IN_DATE\\", \\"SBCNT_SIZE\\", \\"UNIT_COST\\", \\"UNIT_COST_TYP\\", \\"PROCESSING_COST\\", \\"MATERIAL_COST\\", \\"OTHER_OVERHEADS\\") " +"values " +" (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, TO_DATE(?), 0, TO_NUMBER(?), ?, TO_NUMBER(?), TO_NUMBER(?), TO_NUMBER(?))"

"select " +" M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"MODIFY_COUNT\\" as \\"MODIFY_COUNT\\" " +"from " +" M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST " +"where " +" M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"VEND_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"PROC_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"EFF_PHASE_IN_DATE\\" = TO_DATE(?) " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"SBCNT_SIZE\\" = 0 " +"for update nowait"

"select " +" M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST_H.\\"MODIFY_COUNT\\" as \\"MODIFY_COUNT\\" " +"from " +" M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST_H " +"where " +" M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST_H.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST_H.\\"VEND_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST_H.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST_H.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST_H.\\"PROC_CD\\" = ? " +"for update nowait"
"insert into " +" M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST_H(\\"COMPANY_CD\\", \\"VEND_CD\\", \\"PLANT_CD\\", \\"ITEM_CD\\", \\"PROC_CD\\", \\"VEND_ITEM_CD\\") " +"values " +" (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?)"

"update " +" M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST " +"set " +" \\"UNIT_COST\\" = ?, " +" \\"UNIT_COST_TYP\\" = ?, " +" \\"PROCESSING_COST\\" = ?, " +" \\"MATERIAL_COST\\" = ?, " +" \\"OTHER_OVERHEADS\\" = ? " +"where " +" M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"VEND_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"PROC_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"EFF_PHASE_IN_DATE\\" = TO_DATE(?) " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"SBCNT_SIZE\\" = 0"

"select " +" M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"MODIFY_COUNT\\" as \\"MODIFY_COUNT\\" " +"from " +" M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST " +"where " +" M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"VEND_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"PROC_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"EFF_PHASE_IN_DATE\\" = TO_DATE(?) " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"SBCNT_SIZE\\" = 0 " +"for update nowait"

"delete from " +" M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST " +"where " +" M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"VEND_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"PROC_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"EFF_PHASE_IN_DATE\\" = TO_DATE(?) " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"SBCNT_SIZE\\" = 0"

"update " +" M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST_H " +"set " +" \\"VEND_ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +"where " +" M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST_H.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST_H.\\"VEND_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST_H.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST_H.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST_H.\\"PROC_CD\\" = ?"

"select " +" M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST_H.\\"MODIFY_COUNT\\" as \\"MODIFY_COUNT\\" " +"from " +" M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST_H " +"where " +" M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST_H.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST_H.\\"VEND_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST_H.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST_H.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST_H.\\"PROC_CD\\" = ? " +"for update nowait"

"select " +" COUNT(M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"MODIFY_COUNT\\") as \\"RECORD_COUNT\\" " +"from " +" M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST " +"where " +" M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"VEND_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"PROC_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"SBCNT_SIZE\\" = 0"

"delete from " +" M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST " +"where " +" M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"VEND_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"PROC_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"SBCNT_SIZE\\" = 0"

"delete from " +" M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST_H " +"where " +" M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST_H.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST_H.\\"VEND_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST_H.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST_H.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST_H.\\"PROC_CD\\" = ?"

"select " +" M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"ITEM_CD\\" as \\"ITEM_CD\\" " +"from " +" M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST " +"where " +" M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"VEND_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"PROC_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"SBCNT_SIZE\\" = 0 " +"for update nowait"
"SELECT " +" USER_MST.\\"PLANT_CD\\" AS \\"PLANT_CD\\" " +"FROM " +" USER_MST " +"WHERE " +" USER_MST.\\"USER_CD\\" = ?"
"SELECT " +" TO_CHAR(SYS_DATE_CTRL.\\"BUSINESS_OPR_DATE\\", 'YYYY/MM/DD') as \\"BUSINESS_OPR_DATE\\" " +"FROM " +" SYS_DATE_CTRL " +"WHERE " +" SYS_DATE_CTRL.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ?"
"SELECT " +" SYS_PARAMETER.\\"VALUE\\" AS \\"VALUE\\" " +"FROM " +" SYS_PARAMETER " +"WHERE " +" SYS_PARAMETER.\\"NAME\\" = ?"

"SELECT " +" TO_CHAR(M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.EFF_PHASE_IN_DATE,'YYYY/MM/DD') AS EFF_PHASE_IN_DATE, " +" M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.UNIT_COST AS UNIT_COST, " +" M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.UNIT_COST_TYP AS UNIT_COST_TYP, " +" M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.PROCESSING_COST AS PROCESSING_COST, " +" M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.MATERIAL_COST AS MATERIAL_COST, " +" M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.OTHER_OVERHEADS AS OTHER_OVERHEADS " +"FROM " +" M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST " +"WHERE " +" M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ? " +" AND M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"VEND_CD\\" = ? " +" AND M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" AND M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"PROC_CD\\" = ? " +" AND M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"EFF_PHASE_IN_DATE\\" = ? " +" AND M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"SBCNT_SIZE\\" = 0 " +" AND M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ?"
